[00:51] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Cosvid, which we just recently put through its paces, doesn\'t just stop at speed, it also boosts the coherence of your videos. So, if you\'re using an image as a reference, bam, it helps keep everything looking smooth and on point.'

[01:05] [scene:talk]
